WEBVTT


01:01:43.241 --> 01:01:44.909 line:85.83%,end
Most people wouldn't

01:01:45.326 --> 01:01:47.954 line:85.83%,end
even dare to touch Northern spies' money.

01:01:50.790 --> 01:01:53.126 line:85.83%,end
I guess you really needed money.

01:01:54.252 --> 01:01:56.170 line:85.83%,end
I'm…

01:01:56.254 --> 01:01:59.549 line:85.83%,end
I'm so sorry. Please spare me.

01:02:03.553 --> 01:02:04.470 line:85.83%,end
Do you want to live?

01:02:09.142 --> 01:02:10.893 line:85.83%,end
Then from now on,

01:02:12.478 --> 01:02:15.022 line:85.83%,end
manage and keep an eye on the hostages.

01:02:17.150 --> 01:02:18.067 line:85.83%,end
Pardon?

01:02:19.068 --> 01:02:20.945 line:85.83%,end
You mean,

01:02:21.028 --> 01:02:22.697 line:85.83%,end
me?

01:02:22.780 --> 01:02:25.158 line:85.83%,end
What? Do you not want to?

01:02:42.258 --> 01:02:44.802 line:85.83%,end
I wasn't giving you a choice.

01:02:44.969 --> 01:02:47.013 line:85.83%,end
I was ordering you.

01:02:54.937 --> 01:02:56.647 line:85.83%,end
I had an older sister.

01:02:58.483 --> 01:03:02.153 line:85.83%,end
She was smart enough for the country
to send her abroad to study.

01:03:03.780 --> 01:03:07.074 line:85.83%,end
So my parents treated me
like some good-for-nothing.

01:03:07.825 --> 01:03:08.910 line:85.83%,end
They only…

01:03:10.953 --> 01:03:12.622 line:85.83%,end
cared about my sister.

01:03:14.999 --> 01:03:17.084 line:85.83%,end
But when she was in Germany,
a Northern spy--

01:03:22.298 --> 01:03:24.550 line:85.83%,end
A North Korean persuaded her to join them.

01:03:26.260 --> 01:03:28.930 line:85.83%,end
Then while she was questioned
for espionage, she died.

01:03:31.849 --> 01:03:33.643 line:85.83%,end
My dad collapsed because of the shock

01:03:33.726 --> 01:03:35.895 line:85.83%,end
and has been in the hospital
for seven years.

01:03:37.355 --> 01:03:38.856 line:85.83%,end
So if I help you

01:03:39.857 --> 01:03:42.235 line:85.83%,end
and end up getting arrested
for espionage too…

01:03:46.447 --> 01:03:50.535 line:85.83%,end
No one outside the dorm will ever find out
that you've helped us. Don't worry.

01:03:52.119 --> 01:03:54.622 line:85.83%,end
But the kids will know.

01:03:56.791 --> 01:03:58.167 line:85.83%,end
Well…

01:04:01.963 --> 01:04:03.464 line:85.83%,end
As I said, don't worry.

01:04:11.848 --> 01:04:14.600 line:85.83%,end
To show that I appreciate
the value of your labor…

01:04:15.184 --> 01:04:16.102 line:85.83%,end
Comrade Joo.

01:04:16.936 --> 01:04:18.771 line:85.83%,end
Give her ten years' salary all at once.

01:04:27.238 --> 01:04:28.197 line:85.83%,end
This will

01:04:29.365 --> 01:04:30.825 line:85.83%,end
keep you safe.

01:05:05.902 --> 01:05:10.197 line:85.83%,end
No one outside the dorm will ever find out
that you've helped us. Don't worry.

01:05:12.533 --> 01:05:14.869 line:85.83%,end
She must be planning to kill all of them.

01:05:17.079 --> 01:05:18.080 line:85.83%,end
If

01:05:18.873 --> 01:05:22.335 line:85.83%,end
I don't accept this offer…

01:05:26.464 --> 01:05:27.882 line:85.83%,end
I'm sure she'll kill me.

01:06:35.241 --> 01:06:37.410 line:85.83%,end
Hey, is Jang Han-na not here yet?

01:06:37.952 --> 01:06:40.204 line:85.83%,end
What's taking her so long?
She left there ages ago!

01:06:40.287 --> 01:06:42.415 line:85.83%,end
Why isn't she here yet?
Do you want to die?

01:06:42.498 --> 01:06:44.458 line:85.83%,end
-Do you? I'll kill you!
-No, sir.

